#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.174"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.174:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.174:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.174:0.3"
msgid "174. Verasutta"
msgstr "174. Threats"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.205"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañca, gahapati, bhayāni verāni appahāya ‘dussīlo’ iti vuccati, nirayañca "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, unless these five dangers and threats are given up, one is "
"said to be unethical, and is reborn in hell."

msgctxt "an5.174:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.174:2.3"
msgid ""
"Pāṇātipātaṃ, adinnādānaṃ, kāmesumicchācāraṃ, musāvādaṃ, "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Killing living creatures, stealing, committing sexual misconduct, lying, and "
"using alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an5.174:2.4"
msgid ""
"imāni kho, gahapati, pañca bhayāni verāni appahāya ‘dussīlo’ iti vuccati, "
"nirayañca upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Unless these five dangers and threats are given up, one is said to be "
"unethical, and is reborn in hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:3.1"
msgid ""
"Pañca, gahapati, bhayāni verāni pahāya ‘sīlavā’ iti vuccati, sugatiñca "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Once these five dangers and threats are given up, one is said to be ethical, "
"and is reborn in heaven."

msgctxt "an5.174:3.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.174:3.3"
msgid ""
"Pāṇātipātaṃ, adinnādānaṃ, kāmesumicchācāraṃ, musāvādaṃ, "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Killing living creatures, stealing, committing sexual misconduct, lying, and "
"using alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an5.174:3.4"
msgid ""
"imāni kho, gahapati, pañca bhayāni verāni pahāya ‘sīlavā’ iti vuccati, "
"sugatiñca upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"Once these five dangers and threats are given up, one is said to be ethical, "
"and is reborn in heaven."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, gahapati, pāṇātipātī pāṇātipātapaccayā diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, pāṇātipātā paṭivirato neva diṭṭhadhammikaṃ bhayaṃ "
"veraṃ pasavati, na samparāyikaṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who kills living creatures creates dangers and threats both in the "
"present life and in lives to come, and experiences mental pain and sadness. "
"Anyone who refrains from killing living creatures creates no dangers and "
"threats either in the present life or in lives to come, and doesn’t "
"experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an5.174:4.2"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭiviratassa evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"So that danger and threat is quelled for anyone who refrains from killing "
"living creatures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:5.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, gahapati, adinnādāyī … pe …."
msgstr "Anyone who steals …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:6.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, gahapati, kāmesumicchācārī … pe …."
msgstr "Anyone who commits sexual misconduct …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:7.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, gahapati, musāvādī … pe …."
msgstr "Anyone who lies …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, gahapati, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānapaccayā diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, "
"samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ "
"paṭisaṃvedeti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato neva diṭṭhadhammikaṃ "
"bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na samparāyikaṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na cetasikaṃ "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who uses alcoholic drinks that cause negligence creates dangers and "
"threats both in the present life and in lives to come, and experiences "
"mental pain and sadness. Anyone who refrains from using alcoholic drinks "
"that cause negligence creates no dangers and threats either in the present "
"life or in lives to come, and doesn’t experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an5.174:8.2"
msgid ""
"Surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratassa evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ "
"hotīti."
msgstr ""
"So that danger and threat is quelled for anyone who refrains from using "
"alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.1"
msgid "Yo pāṇamatipāteti,"
msgstr "A person in the world kills living creatures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.2"
msgid "musāvādañca bhāsati;"
msgstr "speaks falsely,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.3"
msgid "Loke adinnaṃ ādiyati,"
msgstr "steals,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.4"
msgid "paradārañca gacchati;"
msgstr "commits adultery,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.5"
msgid "Surāmerayapānañca,"
msgstr "and indulges in drinking"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:9.6"
msgid "yo naro anuyuñjati."
msgstr "alcohol and liquor."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:10.1"
msgid "Appahāya pañca verāni,"
msgstr "Unless they give up these five threats,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:10.2"
msgid "dussīlo iti vuccati;"
msgstr "they’re said to be unethical."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:10.3"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā duppañño,"
msgstr "When their body breaks up, that witless person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:10.4"
msgid "nirayaṃ sopapajjati."
msgstr "is reborn in hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.206"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.1"
msgid "Yo pāṇaṃ nātipāteti,"
msgstr "A person in the world doesn’t kill living creatures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.2"
msgid "musāvādaṃ na bhāsati;"
msgstr "speak falsely,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.3"
msgid "Loke adinnaṃ nādiyati,"
msgstr "steal,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.4"
msgid "paradāraṃ na gacchati;"
msgstr "commit adultery,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.5"
msgid "Surāmerayapānañca,"
msgstr "or indulge in drinking"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:11.6"
msgid "yo naro nānuyuñjati."
msgstr "alcohol and liquor."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an5.174:12.1"
msgid "Pahāya pañca verāni,"
msgstr "Giving up these five threats,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:12.2"
msgid "sīlavā iti vuccati;"
msgstr "they’re said to be ethical."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:12.3"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā sappañño,"
msgstr "When their body breaks up, that wise person"

# BB has “heaven” here, which is the normal counterpart of niraya, hell. But the text has sugati, not sagga.
#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.174:12.4"
msgid "sugatiṃ sopapajjatī”ti."
msgstr "is reborn in a good place.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.174:12.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
